{"tha-ap81:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap81:0.2":"Nagasamalavagga ","tha-ap81:0.3":"Thitanjaliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap81:1.1":"“Migaluddo pure asim, ","tha-ap81:1.2":"Aranne kanane aham; ","tha-ap81:1.3":"Tattha addasam sambuddham, ","tha-ap81:1.4":"Battimsavaralakkhanam. ","tha-ap81:2.1":"Tatthaham anjalim katva, ","tha-ap81:2.2":"pakkamim pacinamukho; ","tha-ap81:2.3":"Avidure nisinnassa, ","tha-ap81:2.4":"niyake pannasanthare. ","tha-ap81:3.1":"Tato me asanipato, ","tha-ap81:3.2":"matthake nipati tada; ","tha-ap81:3.3":"Soham maranakalamhi, ","tha-ap81:3.4":"akasim punaranjalim. ","tha-ap81:4.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap81:4.2":"anjalim akarim tada; ","tha-ap81:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap81:4.4":"anjalissa idam phalam. ","tha-ap81:5.1":"Catupannasakappamhi, ","tha-ap81:5.2":"migaketusanamako; ","tha-ap81:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap81:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap81:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap81:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap81:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap81:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma thitanjaliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap81:8.1":"Thitanjaliyattherassapadanam navamam. "}